<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Foreground_and_background_b=
lur">Foreground and background blur</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><spa=
n class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
org/w/index.php?title=3DDepth_of_field&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D13" =
title=3D"Edit section: Foreground and background blur"><span>edit</span></a=
><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>If a subject is at distance <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-s=
tyle:italic;">s</span> and the foreground or background is at distance <spa=
n class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">D</span>, let the dis=
tance between the subject and the foreground or background be indicated by
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
